{
  "text": "The results of stable water isotope analyses are presented in (1964) is an indicator for kinetic (non-equilibrium) fractionation processes and generally related to conditions (i.e. humidity, sea surface temperature, wind speed) in the initial moisture source region [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
